      "para_id": "Q004994.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Nur-Adad , the overseer of the dogs , child of Lugal-urani , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
